{"in": {"title": "Questing Lores", "subtitle": "<span id=\"tr_lore_id\">You, Fangs, and the World</span>", "lines": ["SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/drone-settling-30s.mp3 (no wait)", "NARRATOR: It's morning, and you've just pulled on a jacket and a pair of sneakers and headed out for a hike. The morning air is crisp, the sky serene, and birds are chirping.", "YOU: (to yourself) Today is going to be a great day--", "NARRATOR: And then you stumble over something large, blended in with the orange autumn forest floor. Your heart drops as you slowly turn, realizing it was...warm.", "FANGS: I just want to sleep to 7am! That's all I ask! Why can't I get a full night's sleep before some stick legs steps on me!!", "YOU: (doesn't speak Tiger) Oh. my. god. That's a tiger. That's a tiger in the middle of Los Altos. Well, I guess I'm in the foothills... but that's beside the point!", "FANGS: (does understand Human) Come on, now. I'm not going to eat you.", "YOU: (hyperventilating) What do I who do I call... police? animal control? rangers? red-neck grandpa?", "FANGS: (getting up) For Pete's sake!", "YOU: I'm - where's a stick? Can you fight a tiger with a stick? Why's it huffing it like that?", "FANGS: Huffing?! Just because you're too uncultured to understand me... you know what, I've had enough of this. (stretches then readies to pounce).", "YOU: Uh oh.", "NARRATOR: Fangs leaps forward, lightly gripping you with his jaws, and starts bounding through the forest.", "YOU: (x-loud) AHHHHHHHHHHHHHH!", "FANGS: Ibt habrd do spek wit you im mah mouf bu I'b na going do ead you!", "YOU: (x-loud) AHHHHHHHHHHHHHH!", "FANGS:&nbsp;Ah by glash! Shubt upt aweaby!&nbsp;", "YOU: (x-loud) AHHHHHHHHHHHHHH!", "FANGS: Ah by glash! Shubt upt aweaby!", "NARRATOR: The tiger charges through the forest, through the undergrowth, through that patch of daffodils in the middle of the forest you love, past the pond, all while you dangle out of his mouth. Finally, he drops you unceremoniously.", "NARRATOR: You roll away from the tiger, to your feet.", "YOU: I'm alive! Help! HELP!", "FANGS: (soft) How can someone have so much lung capacity?", "YOU: (bolting on your jello legs) The trees are thinning, I must be near the edge of the forest. Yes! There's a house! HELP!", "NARRATOR: You feel your pockets and they're empty. your phone must've fallen out on the ride.", "YOU: I'll take shelter there and use their house phone to call animal control or the zoo. HELP!", "NARRATOR: You stumble up the front stairs of the house's patio, wipe the remaining tiger saliva off your hands, reach down, and you pound against the front door.", "YOU: (gasping) Help! There's a tiger in the woods! Help!", "NARRATOR: There's no response.", "YOU: (catching your breath, stop for a moment) This house is really short? It's ceilings are weirdly low. I guess I've never been to this side of town but what odd architects thought of this Huh. No, focus. Focus. There is a tiger behind you", "NARRATOR: Fangs comes slowly padding over, looking amused. You pound the door again.", "YOU: (x-loud) Help! Help!", "FANGS: Stop shouting already! I hear you!", "YOU: Oh thank heavens... wait.", "NARRATOR: Yes. You realize the voice that answered came from behind you, not from inside the house. You slowly turn around.", "FANGS: I realize we didn't have a proper introduction after you so rudely woke me. But I'm Fangs.", "YOU: It just... spoke.", "YOU: (faints)", "YOU: Darkness is nice sometimes. It's comforting. And warm. Maybe this was just a bad dream. Oh no. I see light at the end of this darkness. I don't want to wake up.", "NARRATOR: With a shock of adrenaline still pumping through your veins, your eyes pop open.", "YOU: Oh great. It wasn't a dream. Well, it's not every day I wake up with a tiger looking down at me either. A tiger. Wow. What is this world.", "FANGS: Wow, it can speak without shrieking, hooray!", "YOU: A talking tiger. I forgot that part.", "FANGS: (brightly) That's probably because when you heard my lovely voice, you swooned and hit your head on my porch railing.", "YOU: (breathes in deeply, to yourself) What is going on?", "FANGS: I'm so glad you asked. I'm not exactly sure either, to be quite honest. But I think it was one of those nasty tiddlydumpkins that infest that forest. They probably set up some loophole and I'm guessing you got through it.", "YOU: (wasn't expecting one, but will take an answer) Okay. Wow. Alright.", "FANGS: Yes.", "YOU: So what is this place called?", "FANGS: We're really creative when we name things, so our planet is called World.", "YOU: (soft) Hah. Well, then. Hello, world.", "YOU: (slowly) Wait. So you could talk all along and instead of, oh, I don't know, talking! You kidnapped me?!", "FANGS: Woah there. I was talking all along, you just couldn't understand me! I was doing you a favor! I brought you through the laufinlanguagus daffodilius fields. You understand me now, right?", "YOU: Still! I bet there were other ways! I think you just wanted to scare me!", "FANGS: You're really obnoxious, did you know?", "YOU: You're really rude, did you know?", "FANGS: (bares teeth) I think we're going to be great friends. Now let's get you out of this world.", "YOU: And please, of all modes of transport, by your mouth is not one I can handle again.", "FANGS: (ignoring you) I have a friend I can call up that might know something.", "YOU: There are more of you???", "FANGS: Well, he's a bird. But yes.", "NARRATOR: To be continued..."], "speaker_map": {"NARRATOR": "Matthew", "SCENE": "Joanna", "JILL": "Emma", "JACK": "Raveena", "You": "Joey", "Narrator": "Joanna", "Fangs": "Matthew", "To be continued...": "Aditi", "YOU": "Amy", "FANGS": "Brian"}}, "out": {"cache_id": "0f22a70a5d0388649c53add9f0b82240", "audio_objects": [["https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/drone-settling-30s.mp3", 1], ["ce5637c7dc92d14280f09d65d57bfbd0-it-s-morning--and-you-ve----", 0], ["683ae2ec852d2ccee93c55155ea39d92--today-is-going-to-be-a-g